snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Deluxe Edition Available Now!
snippet.description:
Explore every corner of the Far, Far Range with the Slime Rancher: Deluxe Edition - a special retail release NOW AVAILABLE on PS4 and Xbox One!

Every box includes: Full Game, Secret Style Pack DLC, Digital Download for the Original Soundtracks 1 & 2, Coupon for Fangamer Merchandise, and a Slimepedia Booklet.

Buy online or at your local game shop!
https://store.skybound.com/collections/slime-rancher
